title: DC SHOES: MIKE MO TALKS ON THE MIKE MO SIGNATURE SHOE
description:
With a customized design that focuses on fit, protection, board feel, durability, and ventilation, Mike Mo breaks down how his new DC signature shoe was designed from the inside out.



Filmed & Edited By:
Chris Ray
Ryan Loughridge
Tobin Yelland

Song: "Recurring"
By: Bonobo
Courtesy of Ninja Tune
